						               													<description>All the football (soccer) in a card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a card game where you try to have more goals than your opponent. The idea is to start by a draft of 12 card in the center of the table face up. Each player will have 6 to start with at the end of the draft.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You have 6 types of card representing a (or two) football action like :&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     pass&amp;#10;     center&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;etc.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The the player will alternate playing card in a common pile in the middle, the card you play will dicdate which card you opponnent has to play next.&amp;#10;If he don't have the card, he will draw, play if possible.&amp;#10;If he still can't play you will continue your action by playing an other card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;An &amp;quot;unstop&amp;quot; shoot will trigger a goal. BUT wait you have to check the referee by flipping the first card of the draw pile and check if the goal is accepted.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In case of a fault committed (red card), then the player will draw the first card of the pile and get :&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     yellow card (two yellow will remove you a goal)&amp;#10;     free kick (nothing happen)&amp;#10;     penalty (the opponent check the referee for the GOAaaaallll).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The end happen when the pile is depleted twice or at the end of the match if you use the app.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
